2026-05-14T06:41:17.0502772Z 223        <!--
2026-05-14T06:41:17.0503345Z 224            Override Google Play Billing's ProxyBillingActivity so the system
2026-05-14T06:41:17.0504198Z 225            cannot restore it from Recents or after process death with a
2026-05-14T06:41:17.0505054Z 226            stale Intent. The library's onCreate reads the PendingIntent
2026-05-14T06:41:17.0505913Z 227            extra without null-checking; if Android recreates the activity
2026-05-14T06:41:17.0506623Z 228            and the extra is missing, it NPEs on
